+Do not treat it as a normal assistant workspace.
+Do not use archive prompts or invent a new flow.
+
+This is a new sibling runtime variant.
+Do not modify or reinterpret the portable `v2-canon` runtime.
+Do not inspect or reuse `runtime/active-run/*` for this variant.
+Do not inspect or reuse `prompts/v2-canon/*` for this variant.
